{"id":232677235,"title":"聖誕薑餅屋自己做!","content":"http://i.imgur.com/hX7jfje.jpg\n\n 今年聖誕節薑餅屋挑戰從頭做起~~~!!\n\n食譜附上:\n\n食材:\nTommy's軟質餅乾粉 300g\n奶油 60g\n雞蛋 45g\n蛋白霜粉 100g\n水 100g\n糖粉 400g\n製作步驟\n餅乾\n1. 烤爐預熱160℃/140℃。\n2. 將軟質餅乾粉、奶油、雞蛋攪拌均勻成糰。\n3. 麵糰擀成薄片約0.5公分後進爐烤焙20min。\n4. 待餅乾冷卻後切割適當大小即可開始裝飾。\n糖霜\n1. 蛋白霜粉加水打發3分鐘。\n2. 分次加入糖粉拌勻至無粉粒即可。\n組裝裝飾\n1. 分割好餅乾片，使用糖霜當黏著劑使用。\n2. 於餅乾表面使用糖霜做裝飾成下雪後的模樣，再使用糖果、些許翻糖裝飾即可。","excerpt":"今年聖誕節薑餅屋挑戰從頭做起~~~！！，食譜附上：食材：Tommy's軟質餅乾粉 300g，奶油 60g，雞蛋 45g，蛋白霜粉 100g，水 100g，糖粉 400g，製作步驟，餅乾，1. 烤爐預熱","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"11e8d941-0aad-4960-8348-b27c36270fd1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-13T03:02:34.896Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T03:02:34.896Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":7,"tags":[],"topics":["聖誕節","薑餅屋","交換禮物","聖誕禮物","聖誕甜點"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"聖誕CiaoCiao","forumAlias":"merryxmas","school":"銘傳大學","department":"廣告暨策略行銷學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/hX7jfje.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"668caa6b-7dd8-4dda-b880-d833b305a87e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hX7jfjel.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/hX7jfjel.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hX7jfjel.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T03:02:34.896Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T03:02:34.896Z"},{"id":"668caa6b-7dd8-4dda-b880-d833b305a87e","url":"http://i.imgur.com/hX7jfje.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/hX7jfje","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hX7jfjel.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T03:02:34.896Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T03:02:34.896Z"}],"postAvatar":""}